import React from 'react'
import Header from './components/Header'
import CreateNote from './components/CreateNote'
import Footer from './components/Footer'
import Note from './components/Note'

const App = () => {
  return (
    <>
        <Header/>
        <CreateNote  passNote/>
        <Note/>
        <Footer/>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
